qas.question: On what date did the AFL take control of one of its teams?
What team did the league take control of?
Who owned the trademark to the Portland Thunder?
Who is commissioner of the Arena Football League?

context: On <a0_0>January 6, 2016<a0_0/>, the league took over "ownership and operational control" of the <a1_0>Portland Thunder<a1_0/> from its previous owners. On February 3, 2016, it was announced that the franchise will start from scratch and no longer be called the "Thunder" as the name and trademarks belong to former franchise owner <a2_0>Terry Emmert<a2_0/> (similar to the <a3_0>Jerry Jones<a3_0/> move with the Desperados).
